org.semanticweb.yars2.rdfxml

Class RDFXMLParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.semanticweb.yars2.rdfxml.RDFXMLParser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterator<Node[]>

    public class RDFXMLParser
extends Object
implements Iterator<Node[]>
    RDFXMLParser... for... you guessed it... parsing RDF/XML Based on SAXParser. Default behaviour creates a parsing thread which fills a BlockingQueue and is consumed externally through the iterator model. Can use custom CallBack which will not use a seperate thread for parsing and which does not use iterator methods.
    Author:
    aidhog
